Data::IconText
-----------------

This module provides an interface for icon text.
An icon text is a single character that can be rendered alike an icon for a given object.


Pre-Requirements
----------------

On Debian:
$ apt-get install libdist-zilla-plugins-cjm-perl libdist-zilla-plugin-git-perl libdist-zilla-plugin-repository-perl libdist-zilla-plugin-podweaver-perl


Building
--------
$ dzil build
$ dzil install
